      <p>Apart from the delivery of the training, practical instructors will be involved in the <strong>evaluation</strong> of the trainees’ progress through session/daily (<strong>formative</strong>) assessments and could also be involved in the dedicated (<strong>summative</strong>) assessments required at least once at the end of the pre-OJT and OJT training. For formal competence assessments, there is a requirement for practical instructors to hold the <strong>assessor endorsement</strong> as well. </p>

