    <div class="ians-column">

      <h2>Continuation Training Requirements</h2>

      <p>
        <strong>Continuation training</strong>, is designed to maintain the validity of the endorsements of the license and shall consist of <strong>refresher</strong> and <strong>conversion</strong> training courses. It shall be provided according to the requirements contained in the <strong>Unit Competence Scheme</strong> (UCS) as detailed in <strong>ATCO.B.025</strong>
      </p>

      <p>In the graphic below, you can see where the Refresher and Continuation training requirements fit and the UCS requirements that are directly related to Refresher training.</p>

    </div>

    <div class="ians-column-wide-2 oj-s4">
      <div class="oj-s4-title">
        <p>Section 4</p>
        <p>ATCO.D.075</p>
